4-04-11/ty-article/.premium/killing-of-hamas-leaders-sons-wont-torpedo-deal-but-could-postpone-it-more/0000018e-cca9-df04-adae-edfb62350000</guid></item><item><title>以色列基布兹举行逾越节家宴，恳求释放被扣押在加沙地带的人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-kibbutz-sets-up-passover-seder-to-implore-for-release-of-hostages-held-in-gaza/0000018e-cc80-df04-adae-edd2ddd00000</link><description>“带回所有人质，让这个夜晚与众不同”：尼尔·奥兹基布兹成员摆出了一张逾越节家宴桌，上面有 36 张椅子，代表仍被关押在加沙的社区人质</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 10:20:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/israeli-kibbutz-sets-up-passover-seder-to-implore-for-release-of-hostages-held-in-gaza/0000018e-cc80-df04-adae-edd2ddd00000</guid></item><item><title>德国因加沙战争向以色列大屠杀幸存者每人额外提供238美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/germany-to-give-holocaust-survivors-in-israel-an-extra-238-each-because-of-gaza-war/0000018e-cc26-dd23-a3cf-efa76ef10000</link><description>在大屠杀幸存者受到 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击和加沙战争影响后，归还小组负责人表示，德国向以色列大屠杀幸存者额外支付象征性的确认金是一种团结的信息。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 08:43:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/germany-to-give-holocaust-survivors-in-israel-an-extra-238-each-because-of-gaza-war/0000018e-cc26-dd23-a3cf-efa76ef10000</guid></item><item><title>印度尼西亚历史上首次承诺与以色列建立外交关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/indonesia-commits-to-establishing-diplomatic-ties-with-israel-for-first-time-in-history/0000018e-cbfa-dc14-a9de-ebfec78c0000</link><description>世界上最大的穆斯林占多数的国家同意承认以色列，以便加入经合组织——这需要所有成员国的同意——此前以色列官员要求印度尼西亚在批评加沙战争后做出表态。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 08:20:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/indonesia-commits-to-establishing-diplomatic-ties-with-israel-for-first-time-in-history/0000018e-cbfa-dc14-a9de-ebfec78c0000</guid></item><item><title>埃尔多安的独角戏不会说服其他中东领导人抵制以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/erdogans-one-man-show-wont-persuade-other-regional-leaders-to-boycott-israel/0000018e-ca3a-dd23-a3cf-efbfcf390000</link><description>土耳其总统正试图利用加沙战争来提升他作为地区领导人的地位。安卡拉宣布制裁后，以色列和土耳其已经在计算经济成本</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 03:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/erdogans-one-man-show-wont-persuade-other-regional-leaders-to-boycott-israel/0000018e-ca3a-dd23-a3cf-efbfcf390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列试图对敏感的间谍技术保密。已经泄露到国外了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-tried-to-keep-sensitive-spy-tech-under-wraps-it-leaked-abroad/0000018e-c948-d480-a99e-cf5f24900000</link><description>文件显示，由以色列人运营但在以色列出口制度之外运营的 Intellexa 推出了一款基于广告的间谍软件，被认为是以色列进攻性网络的前沿产品</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 03:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-tried-to-keep-sensitive-spy-tech-under-wraps-it-leaked-abroad/0000018e-c948-d480-a99e-cf5f24900000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队向加沙中部发动地面攻势；巴勒斯坦人报告死亡和受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article-live/u-s-could-launch-joint-strike-with-israel-against-iran-senior-official-says/0000018e-caf9-dc93-adce-eef995f30000</link><description>医疗消息人士称，拉法六人在空袭中丧生 ■ 以色列抗议者阻止军队和警察撤走的援助卡车进入 ■ 美国官员：如果伊朗袭击以色列，美国和以色列可能对伊朗进行联合袭击 ■ 胡塞武装控制的也门的 11 架无人机被击落由美军</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 02:41:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-11/ty-article-live/u-s-could-launch-joint-strike-with-israel-against-iran-senior-official-says/0000018e-caf9-dc93-adce-eef995f30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方限制特拉维夫反政府抗议的授权区域；组织者谴责镇压企图</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/police-limit-authorized-zone-of-anti-govt-protest-organizers-decry-suppression-attempt/0000018e-c997-d480-a99e-cfd7d0350000</link><description>警方表示，之所以做出这一决定，是因为上周六前往阿兹列利十字路口参加抗议活动的抗议者人数不足以证明在该地点举行抗议是合理的，该地点是一条主要交通干线。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 20:42:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/police-limit-authorized-zone-of-anti-govt-protest-organizers-decry-suppression-attempt/0000018e-c997-d480-a99e-cfd7d0350000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙的军事“演习”毫无意义的成功</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/israels-military-maneuver-in-gaza-was-a-pointless-success/0000018e-c904-d1b7-a3af-ef0fb2820000</link><description>如果没有可行的策略来遵循，成功的机动就是：为了机动而机动。事后看来，需要进行更有限的地面进攻，这本来可以减少哈马斯和加沙的损失，但之后会给以色列更多的选择</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 19:57:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/israels-military-maneuver-in-gaza-was-a-pointless-success/0000018e-c904-d1b7-a3af-ef0fb2820000</guid></item><item><title>“反犹太血腥诽谤”：伯克利院长举办的私人晚宴遭到反以色列活动人士的攻击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/private-dinner-hosted-by-berkeley-dean-targeted-by-anti-israel-activists/0000018e-c94c-d1b7-a3af-ef4fe2ea0000</link><description>视频显示，一名活动人士在院长家中举行的一次活动中指责伯克利法学院参与种族灭绝，因为该学院投资了与以色列做生意的公司，而该院长最近也出现在反犹太主义漫画中</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 19:39:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/private-dinner-hosted-by-berkeley-dean-targeted-by-anti-israel-activists/0000018e-c94c-d1b7-a3af-ef4fe2ea0000</guid></item><item><title>犹太复国主义者到底是什么？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-10/ty-article/.highlight/what-the-hell-is-a-zionist/0000018e-c913-dd23-a3cf-ef971e240000</link><description>“犹太复国主义者”这个词现在遍布互联网上的帖子和评论部分。这是当我在社交媒体网站 X 上询问人们这意味着什么时发生的事情</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 19:34:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-10/ty-article/.highlight/what-the-hell-is-a-zionist/0000018e-c913-dd23-a3cf-ef971e240000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方在导致哈马斯领导人三名儿子死亡的空袭之前没有向政府通报情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-airstrike-in-gaza-kills-three-sons-of-hamas-political-leader-haniyeh/0000018e-c890-d1b7-a3af-ef9f0cc70000</link><description>巴勒斯坦报道称哈尼亚的三名孙子也在袭击中丧生，但以色列国防军尚未证实这些报道；袭击发生后，哈尼亚表示：“任何认为针对我的儿子会迫使哈马斯改变立场的人都是妄想”</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 18:26:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-airstrike-in-gaza-kills-three-sons-of-hamas-political-leader-haniyeh/0000018e-c890-d1b7-a3af-ef9f0cc70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 187 天：哈马斯政治领袖哈尼亚的亲属在加沙袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-187-relatives-of-hamas-political-chief-haniyeh-killed-in-gaza-strike/0000018e-c8fe-d480-a99e-ceff5f1e0000</link><description>哈马斯政治领袖伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚的三个儿子和一些孙子在加沙被杀 ■ 大马士革袭击后，以色列和伊朗官员相互威胁 ■ 拜登表示，他不同意内塔尼亚胡总理对加沙战争的态度 ■ 美国：尚未收到拉法入侵的通知撤离平民的日期或计划 ■ 这是战争开始 187 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 17:31:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-187-relatives-of-hamas-political-chief-haniyeh-killed-in-gaza-strike/0000018e-c8fe-d480-a99e-ceff5f1e0000</guid></item><item><title>“我们请求您的原谅”：定居者参加被以色列预备役军人枪杀的巴勒斯坦皈依犹太教的葬礼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/settlers-attend-funeral-of-palestinian-convert-to-judaism-who-was-shot-by-idf-reservist/0000018e-c875-d480-a99e-ce7727a00000</link><description>大卫·本·亚伯拉罕 (David Ben Avraham) 现年 63 岁，原名 Sameh Zeitoun，几年前皈依犹太教。据报道，他在前往耶路撒冷的途中被以色列预备役军人开枪打死。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 16:44:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/settlers-attend-funeral-of-palestinian-convert-to-judaism-who-was-shot-by-idf-reservist/0000018e-c875-d480-a99e-ce7727a00000</guid></item><item><title>不要指望内塔尼亚胡会达成人质交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/dont-expect-a-hostage-deal-from-netanyahu/0000018e-c885-dc93-adce-eef53c8d0000</link><description>和许多以色列人一样，在我们自己的总理的帮助下，人质协议的希望不断破灭，我感到筋疲力尽。内塔尼亚胡对自己的人民没有责任感，包括被原教旨主义、世界末日的哈马斯扣押在不人道条件下的人质。每一天似乎都让我们更进一步，而不是更接近突破</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 16:32:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/dont-expect-a-hostage-deal-from-netanyahu/0000018e-c885-dc93-adce-eef53c8d0000</guid></item><item><title>这位以色列人的丈夫在加沙被扣为人质，她正试图拯救基布兹仅存的一切</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/anyone-who-doesnt-want-to-pay-a-price-should-not-let-his-citizens-be-taken-hostage/0000018e-c7f7-d1b7-a3af-e7ff10dc0000</link><description>在 10 月 7 日被绑架之前，Chaim Peri 救出了他的妻子 Osnat，她是 Nir ​​Oz 基布兹的主席。从那时起，她一边领导着一个支离破碎的社区，一边为他的自由而战。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 16:09:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/anyone-who-doesnt-want-to-pay-a-price-should-not-let-his-citizens-be-taken-hostage/0000018e-c7f7-d1b7-a3af-e7ff10dc0000</guid></item><item><title>前立法者、电影制片人荣获以色列终身成就奖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/former-lawmaker-filmmaker-to-receive-israel-prize-for-lifetime-achievement/0000018e-c832-dc93-adce-ee7202190000</link><description>教育部表示，在前议员埃德娜·索洛达尔去世的消息宣布后，奖励委员会就向部长提出了授予她奖项的建议。行业领军人物埃德里与内塔尼亚胡家族关系密切</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 16:03:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/former-lawmaker-filmmaker-to-receive-israel-prize-for-lifetime-achievement/0000018e-c832-dc93-adce-ee7202190000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方考虑调查特拉维夫大学教授赞扬瓦利德·达卡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/police-weigh-investigating-israeli-scholar-for-eulogizing-palestinian-security-prisoner/0000018e-c80a-d1b7-a3af-ef0fb7480000</link><description>阿纳特·马塔尔教授赞扬了达卡，这位服刑时间最长的巴勒斯坦安全囚犯本周因癌症去世，引发了要求解雇她的呼声，并引发警方以“煽动”罪名进行调查。以色列教育部长告诉大学校长：“我希望你们尽快采取严厉行动”</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:33:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/police-weigh-investigating-israeli-scholar-for-eulogizing-palestinian-security-prisoner/0000018e-c80a-d1b7-a3af-ef0fb7480000</guid></item></channel></rss>